{"type":"article","id":422,"title":"知乎：对抗删帖，你需要互联网存档神器 archive","uid":1,"topics":[6,57,114],"contents":"<b>作者：胡鞍钢</b><br>\n<br>\n（原文已删除，<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180730235019/https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/40920749\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">存档链接</a>）<br>\n<br>\n众所周知，我们使用的互联网是个很有特色的东西，正常的互联网只会遗忘那些没什么人访问的内容，我们的互联网却经常在热点事件发生的时候，把最热门的文章吸入黑洞。<br>\n<br>\n今天介绍一款删前留痕的神器，archive.today. 我所知道的域名有三个 <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180730235019/https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//archive.today\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://archive.today</a>, <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180730235019/https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//archive.is\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://archive.is</a>, <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180730235019/https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//archive.fo\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://archive.fo</a><br>\n<br>\n用法很简单，想保存的链接加入红框即可存档，如果某个链接已经变成 404，你只能祈祷之前有人存档了那篇文章，把链接贴到下面的黑框里试试。<br>\n<br>\n示例：<br>\n（存档知乎答案的效果）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/c3YN8Ez.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c3YN8Ez.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/c3YN8Ez.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n（存档微信文章的效果）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/BUi7QH0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BUi7QH0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/BUi7QH0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n当然了，这么好用的神器，待遇自然会跟 Google YouTube Wikipedia 一样，遇到<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7AeoRLM.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7AeoRLM.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7AeoRLM.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n但我相信这是拦不住聪明的知乎用户的。<br>\n<br>\n（注，还有个神器，叫 archive.org, 能存档很多网页，甚至网页的不同版本，但是很遗憾，他们出于对 robot.txt 的尊重，不存微信公众号，微博文章，和知乎答案，所以本文只介绍 archive.today）","date":"2019-01-16","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}